    <subfield code="a">34 pages, published (splitted into two distinct pieces) in the proceedings of the '7th spring school and workshop on quantum field theory &amp; Hamiltonian systems' and of the '6th mathematical physics meeting: summer school and conference on modern mathematical physics', v2: references (and related comments) added</subfield>
